name: Legends Token
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Legends LG is a state of art gamefi project on Arbitrum chain.

What makes your project unique?
LG is planning to launch the No.1 GameFi on the ARB chain, and the ecosystem has been largely deployed. Our unique SocialFi element in our game makes it accessible to all gamers, users can ear rewards using our socialfi for free and then redeeming these rewards in our game

History of your project.
We launched on 23 April 2023

What’s next for your project?
We are about to launch our airdrop campaign followed by our GameFi launch

What can your token be used for?
LG tokens can be used in our GameFi
